<p>
The Modern variant was created by Vincent Mous, who described it in
a series of articles for <a href=<POUCH>>The Diplomatic Pouch</A> Zine,
beginning with <a href=<POUCH>/Zine/W1995A/Mous/Modern.html>Modern Times</a>.

